I"O<p><strong>Achieving the Dream</strong> partners with community colleges to design and share innovative programs (interventions) to improve student success. ATD asked Crow Insight to develop a visual interface for its Interventions Showcase. The new Showcase both summarizes the hundreds of interventions conducted and helps colleges discover more about each.</p>

<p>We recommended the “tree map” format because it is intuitive and can accommodate large numbers of categories. Tree maps reduce the ability to compare exact quantities, but such comparisons were not a priority here.</p>
